ines in Binmaley, Pangasinan}}\n\n==Images==\n<gallery perrow=3>\nFile:Binmaley56788jf.JPG|The Our Lady of the Purification Parish Church\nFile:Binmaley567yjf.JPG|Binmaley Museum\nFile:Binmaley567wjf.JPG|Binmaley Presidencia [http://www.pangasinan.org/binmaley/]\nFile:Binmaley567cjf.JPG|Bulwagan ng Sangguniang Bayan at Himpilan ng Pambansang Kapulisan\nFile:Binmaley567bjf.JPG|Pamilihang Bayan ng Binmaley\nFile:Binmaley567jf.JPG|Manat river & Gumapos Bridge\n</gallery>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170702105401/http://www.competitive.org.ph/cmcindex/pages/profile/?lgu=Binmaley Municipal Profile at the National Competitiveness Council of the Philippines]\n* [http://pangasinan.gov.ph/the-province/cities-and-municipalities/binmaley/ Binmaley at Pangasinan Government Website]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20161010201809/http://www.blgs.gov.ph/lgpmsv2/cmshome/index.php?pageID=23 Local Governance Performance Management System]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120413163013/http://www.nscb.gov.ph/activestats/psgc/default.asp Philippine Standard Geographic Code]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20081120024509/http://www.census.gov.ph/data/census2007/index.html Philippine Census Information]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20130624083039/https://www.pangasinan.org/binmaley/  Pangasinan.org : Binmaley Family and School Reunion Archives]\n\n{{Geographic location\n | Centre    = Binmaley\n | North     = ''[[Lingayen Gulf]]''\n | East      = [[Dagupan]]\n | Southeast = [[Calasiao, Pangasinan|Calasiao]]\n | South     = [[San Carlos, Pangasinan|San Carlos]]\n | West      = [[Lingayen, Pangasinan|Lingayen]]\n}}\n{{Pangasinan}}\n\n[[Category:Municipalities of Pangasinan]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                   = {{PH wikidata|name}}\n| image_skyline          = Binmaley Pangasinan.JPG\n| image_caption          = \n| image_flag             = \n| image_seal             = Binmaley Pan